data.description: Spacious move-in-ready 3/2/2 in the West end of Beaumont on beautiful large lot.  Completely remodeled in 2019 and just recently totally painted inside.  Soothing tones of gray and white with gold fixtures give it a very modern feel.  Tile floors throughout, quartz countertops in kitchen and baths, large living room with fireplace.  Open concept kitchen, breakfast and living room, extra room in back for den or extra living/dining combo.  Inside utility room, master bedroom has full bath with soaker tub, double sinks and separate shower.  The master bedroom walk-in closet is everyone's dream.  Totally fenced yard, extra parking with RV cover, beautiful mature trees.
